{"tid":1722971,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(學術討論) 《義勇軍進行曲》嘅歌詞正正就係鼓勵人反抗","createTime":"2019-11-15T05:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T19:03:04.000Z","uid":249653,"like":58,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ed00adc784c5341c1b66ca81c1342ea4d820e9","tid":1722971,"uid":249653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"之前都有人講過，其實國歌幾諷刺，日日唱緊首歌嘅正正就係甘願做奴隸、唔敢出聲嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n策略性咁講，要唱未必個個肯，但如果將首歌部份嘅字眼融入文宣入面(e.g. 起來 / 唔好做奴隸 / 築起血肉長城 / 冒著炮火前進)，會唔會可以做到潛移默化嘅效果，令啲藍絲一唱就諗起我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《義勇軍進行曲》- 曲: 聶耳  詞: 田漢<br />\n<em>起來！<br />\n不願做奴隸的人們！<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！<br />\n中華民族到了最危險的時候，<br />\n每個人被迫著發出最後的吼聲。<br />\n起來！<br />\n起來！<br />\n起來！<br />\n我們萬眾一心，冒著敵人的炮火前進！<br />\n冒著敵人的炮火前進！<br />\n前進！<br />\n前進！進！</em>"},{"pid":"4881c7e695090e44e3a8bf9265c50a721a78137b","tid":1722971,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"想改詞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2771c7a6e27028ccc0c5538990bf02e8c3d6ef18","tid":1722971,"uid":165336,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"索性用黎幫義士整mv激鳩死藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83766f802c4466b855863a4f56056b8305f490ce","tid":1722971,"uid":254208,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"推到國歌唔唱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2c9385d012bfcfd2d4642d13bc30a898a0c658","tid":1722971,"uid":55511,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"係微博講多少少應該連國歌都禁撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2bbef6a8e1ba99766ce27e26e77248eaa6d114","tid":172297